  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Westerlands.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The westerlands and the location of Deep Den\"><img alt=\"The westerlands and the location of Deep Den\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7f/The_Westerlands.png/300px-The_Westerlands.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7f/The_Westerlands.png/450px-The_Westerlands.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7f/The_Westerlands.png/600px-The_Westerlands.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 54.4%; left: 63.3%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 10px; font-size: 10px;\"><img alt=\"The westerlands and the location of Deep Den\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/10px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Deep Den\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/15px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/20px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 100%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Deep Den</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">The <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a> and the location of Deep Den\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Deep Den</b> is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lydden\" title=\"House Lydden\">House Lydden</a> in the eastern <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is located in hilly and mountainous terrain east of <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a>, with <a href=\"/index.php/Hornvale\" title=\"Hornvale\">Hornvale</a> to the north and <a href=\"/index.php/Silverhill\" title=\"Silverhill\">Silverhill</a> to the south.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The <a href=\"/index.php/Goldroad\" title=\"Goldroad\">Goldroad</a> passes nearby.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Deep_den_franz.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/68/Deep_den_franz.jpg/350px-Deep_den_franz.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"232\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/6/68/Deep_den_franz.jpg 1.5x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Deep_den_franz.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Deep Den, by Franz Miklis © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<div style=\"clear:both;\"></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deep_Den&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=